    <title>Can't define scale in blob</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">In the next link http://publib.boulder.ibm.com/infocenter/db2luw/v8/index.jsp?topic=/com.ibm.db2.udb.doc/admin/r0000927.htm you can see how to create tables in the case of blob and clob you can define de scale you know 10K, 10 M or 10 G even the string NOT LOGGED for biggest files hibernate doesn't support this.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">In &lt;property name="file" type="blob"  not-null="false" length="200000" &gt;&lt;/property&gt; you can only specify on length attribute numbers.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
